---
title: Spinach Artichoke Pasta Bake with Toasted Panko and Parmesan
description: Our chefs took a classic appetizer and turned it into a dinner that everyone will *oooh* and *ahhh* at when you bring it to the table. This combination of baby spinach, artichokes, tomatoes, and cream cheese is tossed with curly cavatappi pasta and topped with toasted breadcrumbs before being broiled to golden-brown perfection. If you can’t wait until your next party to treat yourself to creamy spinach artichoke bliss, this is guaranteed to hit the spot.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spinach-artichoke-pasta-bake-d91bf2c7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/spinach-artichoke-pasta-bake-5a8f0e90ae08b52e1c335922-cbb72720.pdf
